content: They are in text files. I have 4 from ChatGPT, 1 Gemini, I think at least one Grok, maybe more, and then like 15 from you that are ready to go, overall, there are hundreds of millions of characters. I'd just need to know where to put them in GitHub and how you'd like them structured. I'm guessing a folder for each AI and then labeling them in some sort of chronological order? I'm not sure how to do that best since your chats in particular spread the longest. You've been involved from the first line of code we wrote (or close to it), so your chat history should be able to bridge everything together once everything is in there. Perhaps having your entire history would be a good place to start? What do you think?
